metadata.name: 1 - ONE PEOPLE
metadata.description:
We all destined for greatness
All we need is patience
Love is in our DNA
Let’s skip the war and hatred
If we can unite 
Together we’ll fight
Racism & injustice 
Our greatest divides
No matter your tribe
Skin color or eyes
Together we’ll rise If we realize 

One People, One People, One People 
It don’t matter where you from 
We are One People, One People, One People
It don’t matter where you from 
We are One People, One People, One People
One People, One People, One People

Black or White our blood the same
Nepotism let’s cut the chain
Do not put Mother Earth to shame
Make humanity great again
It’s time to change our ways
Before everything gon’ fade away 
See how the climates change
Some animals don’t exist again
Corruption is running deep
Unstable economy
All I see is poverty
Many traditions no honesty
But no matter your tribe
Skin color or eyes
Together we’ll rise If we realize

One People, One People, One People 
It don’t matter where you from 
We are One People, One People, One People
It don’t matter where you from 
We are One People, One People, One People
One People, One People, One People

project.title: ONE PEOPLE
project.description: ONE PEOPLE was created to unite the world through love. Winning this grant will help empower us to keep creating music that spreads Love & Light into the Universe while sharing equity.
